  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/a939385a0ed2e6c30a14cc19f5d738d9.avif?t=1727851228\" width=630 height=242 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/84ccf06b343026a5ed73cb1e1cf7c1d2.poster.avif?t=1727851228\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/84ccf06b343026a5ed73cb1e1cf7c1d2.webm?t=1727851228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/84ccf06b343026a5ed73cb1e1cf7c1d2.mp4?t=1727851228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/dc48acfd4e5b4c97f35641cbe36f5b37.poster.avif?t=1727851228\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/dc48acfd4e5b4c97f35641cbe36f5b37.webm?t=1727851228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/dc48acfd4e5b4c97f35641cbe36f5b37.mp4?t=1727851228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In Mononeko, players seamlessly weave button presses into the game’s musical beat, creating an immersive dance of attack and movement. With rhythmic precision, players hone their aim to vanquish foes and chain together an endless sequence of commands, but a single misstep can unravel your progress. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/0918c33de8dd9aa1a6ea8295e980f275.avif?t=1727851228\" width=630 height=242 /></span><br>Along your journey, you’ll revive fallen kittens to bolster your ranks and gain boons for increased firepower. Time is of the essence as you race to catch the humans before they elude your grasp!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/90b2be9ddbae35216c78b90f478ca0af.avif?t=1727851228\" width=630 height=242 /></span><br>Every day, the streets witness a growing number of abandoned cats. Embark on a heartfelt odyssey and embody the spirits of these cats to confront humans with the consequences of their neglect, exposing a grim mystery behind the feline abandonment and mistreatment, and ignite a spark of change in your pursuit of retribution.",
