eight=242 /></span><br>Along your journey, you’ll revive fallen kittens to bolster your ranks and gain boons for increased firepower. Time is of the essence as you race to catch the humans before they elude your grasp!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458120/extras/90b2be9ddbae35216c78b90f478ca0af.avif?t=1727851228\" width=630 height=242 /></span><br>Every day, the streets witness a growing number of abandoned cats. Embark on a heartfelt odyssey and embody the spirits of these cats to confront humans with the consequences of their neglect, exposing a grim mystery behind the feline abandonment and mistreatment, and ignite a spark of change in your pursuit of retribution.",
